{"id":953,"date":"2020-01-15T07:03:58","date_gmt":"2020-01-15T07:03:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/?page_id=953"},"modified":"2021-09-02T05:43:15","modified_gmt":"2021-09-02T05:43:15","slug":"code-of-conduct","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/code-of-conduct\/","title":{"rendered":"Code of Conduct"},"content":{"rendered":"\n\t<section class=\"section\" id=\"section_441333472\">\n\t\t<div class=\"bg section-bg fill bg-fill  \" >\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"section-bg-overlay absolute fill\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"section-content relative\">\n\t\t\t\n\n<div class=\"row row-collapse align-middle\"  id=\"row-2059271956\">\n\n\n\t<div id=\"col-737123691\" class=\"col small-12 large-12\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n<div class=\"container section-title-container\" ><h1 class=\"section-title section-title-normal\"><b><\/b><span class=\"section-title-main\" style=\"color:rgb(0, 149, 232);\"><i class=\"icon-star-o\" ><\/i>Code of conduct<\/span><b><\/b><\/h1><\/div>\n\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#col-737123691 > .col-inner {\n  margin: 0px 0px -15px 0px;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-433993922\" class=\"col medium-8 small-12 large-8\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t<div id=\"text-3785922054\" class=\"text\">\n\t\t\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In order to create a positive atmosphere in our school we expect all members of the school community to:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Show respect for the needs and differences of all individuals<\/li>\n<li>Respect the property of to others, the school and the local community by treating the environment with care.<\/li>\n<li>Be excellent representatives of the school at all times take responsibility for their own actions.<\/li>\n<li>Acknowledge that everyone is entitled to be happy and to feel secure and calm in a community free from aggression and bullying.<\/li>\n<li>Make a positive contribution to life at the School.<\/li>\n<li>Bring only suitable and appropriate items into the School.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>The code was developed to help us achieve our Mission Statement and to make SunUp a happy, stimulating and enjoyable Centre of learning.<\/strong><\/p>\n\t\t\n<style>\n#text-3785922054 {\n  color: rgb(0,0,0);\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n\t<div id=\"col-322947164\" class=\"col medium-4 small-12 large-4\"  >\n\t\t<div class=\"col-inner\"  >\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\n\t<div class=\"img has-hover x md-x lg-x y md-y lg-y\" id=\"image_833077099\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-inner dark\" >\n\t\t\t<img width=\"980\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-980x1024.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-980x1024.png 980w, https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-287x300.png 287w, https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-768x803.png 768w, https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-1469x1536.png 1469w, https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Sunup-Logo-1959x2048.png 1959w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<style>\n#image_833077099 {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\n\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\n\n<\/div>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\n<style>\n#section_441333472 {\n  padding-top: 30px;\n  padding-bottom: 30px;\n}\n#section_441333472 .section-bg-overlay {\n  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);\n}\n#section_441333472 .section-bg.bg-loaded {\n  background-image: url(https:\/\/sunup.edu.bd\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/SunUp-Book-Background.jpg);\n}\n#section_441333472 .section-bg {\n  background-position: 84% 37%;\n}\n<\/style>\n\t